Add @olie{2-3%spsk} to a #pot. Fry @finthakket løg{0.5%dl}, @knust hvidløg{1-2%fed}, @gulerod{1%dl} and @bladselleri{0.5%dl}. Add @hakket oksekød{0.25%kg} and stir until it has separated and lost its color. Add @laurbærblad{1}, @oregano{}, @timian{}, @salt{}, @peber{}, and @muskat{1/8-1/4%tsk}. Add optionally @reven citronskal{}. Pour in @tør hvidvin{2.5%dl} or @bouillon{2.5%dl}, add @tomatpuré{2%spsk} and @tomater{4%fl.}. Bring to a simmer, then cover and simmer for ~{20%minutes}. Remove the @laurbærblad{}. Let the dish simmer for approx. ~{10%minutes} more.